  RAPES - AN  IMMEDIATE
                 CONCERN  OF  MANKIND

In 2022, the total number of rape cases reported in India amounted to over 31 thousand. 
As of the last update in January 2022, rape reports in India have been a matter of significant concern. The National Crime Records Bureau (NCRB) data typically shows an increasing trend in reported cases of rape over the years, which can be attributed to several factors, including increased awareness, changes in reporting practices, and better access to justice for survivors. However, it's essential to note that the reported numbers may not accurately reflect the true prevalence of rape, as many cases still go unreported.

 ARMOR is a comprehensive women's safety app designed to empower and protect women as they navigate their daily lives. With a user-friendly interface and an array of innovative features, ARMOR is your go-to tool for enhancing personal safety and peace of mind.​
ARMOR is more than just a safety app; it's a movement—an unwavering commitment to empowering women, fostering solidarity, and creating a world where every woman feels safe, respected, and free to pursue her dreams without compromise.

KNOW  YOUR  APP!!!

YOU WANT IT? WE GOT IT


FEATURES INCORPORATED IN OUR APP:
 

1. We made an app which sends http requests to the server which holds current locations of individual users, police stations and details of emergency contacts.
 

2. Furthermore, the app has 3 additional features in the form of buttons:
 

Panic Button: Instantly alerts emergency contacts, nearest police stations, and individuals within a radius of 1 km with live GPS tracking.
 

Warning Button: Allows cautious signaling, escalating to a panic alert if not cancelled within a set timer
(when the victim is uncertain of the danger)
 

Alert Button: On-demand sharing of live location with designated contacts.

WHO CAN USE
THE APP!!!

Our app is designed for women of all ages and backgrounds who seek to enhance their personal safety and well-being. Whether you're a student walking home late at night, a professional commuting to work, a traveler exploring new places, or anyone else concerned about your safety, our app is here to support you. We welcome women from all walks of life who prioritize their safety and want access to tools and resources to help them feel more secure in their daily lives.

Introducing the "SafeSphere" a revolutionary women's safety gadget designed to provide unparalleled protection and peace of mind in any situation. Compact yet powerful, this sleek device seamlessly integrates into your daily life, offering discreet security at your fingertips.

The SafeSphere is more than just a gadget—it's your personal bodyguard, always vigilant and ready to respond to any threat. With its advanced sensors , it continuously monitors your surroundings, detecting potential dangers and alerting you to any suspicious activity nearby.

But the SafeSphere doesn't stop there. Equipped with a powerful alarm system , it serves as a powerful deterrent, warding off would-be attackers and drawing attention to your situation. In the event of an emergency, a simple press of a button triggers a loud alarm , instantly attracting help and giving you precious moments to escape.

What sets the SafeSphere apart is its discreet design and that it comes in the form of a pendant.
